comments: ["This is about the 5th or 6th time that I'm giving this app a try and using a premium account to monitor my pet while I'm on vacation. EACH time I've used it the same problem occurres -  The app works perfectly for 2-3 days, then suddenly stops connecting to the camera. I am extremely disappointed with the app, I will be looking for other alternatives, which is a shame since when the app did work it worked extremely well, but it has proven to be unreliable time and time again.", "I got access to the premium version after doing a pretend review and am updating it now after using it. Functions really well, and really helpful for my dog with seperation anxiety. Only suggestion I would make is it would be great to see a snippet of video with the noise activity log! As is I can't figure out what she is barking at. For this reason I won't pay the premium price for ongoing use as I really need that feature. But if you want real time video then it works great", "Since signing up with the premium app earlier this week I have experienced nothing but problems, it keeps disconnecting and the camera doesn't work. When I was just using the free version I had alot more success with this App. Kinda frustrated and disappointed that I spend the money on this", "It's okay. I think there are better apps. I wish I could set what frequencies it picks up. It constantly tells me my dog is being noisy when it's just the jingle of his collar. Lowering the sensitivity then doesn't pick up his barking. Which makes the notifications just really annoying and constant. The 'just hearing sound' mode is cool but immediately turns off when my screen turns off or I open another app. It needs to stay active, that's the whole point. Might as well stare at the video.", "a little buggy but otherwise good. the audio and motion settings continuously show as 'not set' despite being set. I'm not sure if it exists, or couldn't find it, but there's no option to extend the video in the activity log(?)", "Very good app, it would be nice if the audio commands used the default microphone instead of just the main phone one though, so I could use my earbuds to set commands/talk to my dog. My phone mic doesn't work. Would've contacted support, but there's no support email", "This is a great app, works better than some of the actual pet cams, at a cheaper price and without annoying hardware to set up. My only problem is that the background monitoring is so hidden away. I like to use background monitoring at night while my phone is on charge. But I don't need that during the day at work, notifications are perfect then. So it means I have to trawl through 3 settings screens twice a day. If you put this option in an easy location, it would make this a 5⭐ app for me.", "Absolutely wonderful! The app is flawless in my opinion. I had an issue and reached out to them and they not only took care of the problem immediately but gave me 3 months for free. They really care about people and it warms my heart. You don't see that much anymore. Thank you 🙏 ❤️ 😊 my little furbabies thank you too!!", 'Amazing app to watch my puppy. Night vision with on/off torch feature is a great bonus. The app tells me when my puppy makes a noise or moves around, I like that I can adjust the notifications from low to high sensitivity. Records sounds and images in an activity log which I can then save. No problems with the app so far. Thank you.', 'Seems to work well enough for cats even though many features are designed for dogs. My home station failed less than 1 day into our trip but that may have been a hardware issue.', 'The app is very easy to use, and very effective, carefully designed. Used it to monitor my senior dog while working with his separation anxiety. Can be monitored by 2 devices simultaneously. Very convenient to be able to play prerecorded messages. Very useful the ability to monitor without sound on (i.e. during meetings).', 'App is very convenient to setup and to use , living in a country where upload speed is severly limited , would love to see an option for limited speeds especially when rewatching a recording', "It's decent and works for what it is needed for my mic is super sensitive it seems like at the lowest setting I can pickup myself walking down the stairs and I'm not very loud doing so.so it works!only reason for 4 stats is because it's not just my 1 phone but all phone mics are extremely sensitive and send alot of false notifications.", "Admittedly, I have only tried for a short time so far, but it was easy to set up and seems very easy to use. Just what I needed for a rare occasion when my boy doesn't go with me.", 'I just downloaded this but it seems to be working well on the free trial. My ads were in French and it was hard to figure out how to click out of it because there was no X. Just a question in French and it kept taking me to a website ad when I clicked the wrong word to end the ad.', "Today's update got stuck at installing, had to reinstall. Before this update: Light detection set to auto but have to turn it on and off. Motion detection stops working at times. Have to force stop dog station and restart it for it to work. Happened several times.", "Such a great app! We just moved overseas with our Cane Corso. So he's had a lot of anxiety with the flight and separation anxiety. Doesn't help that we're also in a hotel room where we leave him in a crate. He's used to having free roam of the house. This app is a lifesaver and gives us peace of mind that our dog is not only safe but not too stressed because he can hear our voice. Such a simple setup as well. Using our android phone connected to our IPad left in the room in front of his crate.", "just downloaded the appHoping it's easy to navigate and actually free to monitor without having to pay. UPDATE. SO FAR IT SEEMS TO BE WORKING. I WILL MAKE A FINAL REVIEW ONCE IM AWAY FROM THE HOUSE TRYOMG TO CONNECT. From experience that always seems to be an issue...", "When it works, it's fabulous. Unfortunately a good amount of times I try to use it, it won't show any video, won't play back audio, or disconnects itself entirely.", "It's very convenient and easy to use! I love that I can talk to and see my dogs and I can just use an old phone! I wish it had a better viewing angle like a wideframe or able to scan more of the room but it's not bad! I really enjoy it and have only had it a week or so", 'Very simple to pair your devices and start monitoring right away!! The video is very clear, crisp and clean. Absolutely no regrets and highly recommend anyone to try it!!', 'This app is ok. It suits my purpose, but I do have occasional issues of losing connection to the dog station, which can be frustrating. That could be the other phone though and not the app.', 'I would rate 5 if you didnt have to pay for so many features. The free version m has limited capabilities', "I absolutely love this app because I just got my puppy, and I like to be able to watch him while I'm at work!! I'm giving it 4 stars, though, cause not everyone can afford the premium of all these apps . Oh, and cause it's always telling me that the dog camera isn't connected or that he's resting when really he's playing/moving. But other than that I LOVE iT!!! 🥰", 'This app is excellent... great way to monitor your pet without having to install cameras.', "just started using this app. seems stabel, and easy to use. I'll update after a couple of weeks.", "This app is great. It has many features and was helpful when I adopted two puppies in February. I loved the trial version enough to subscribe and found the subscription to be very affordable for what you get. However, I needed something with night vision and the old cellphone I was using didn't have that capability so I had to break down and purchase a webcam. Previously I would turn my home lights on remotely, but it was becoming a hassle. Sometimes I just don't have those extra seconds.", 'I have to give this app 4 star. Even though it stopped working on my way to my vacation, the customer service was stellar. They tried really hard to fix the matter and answered my email fast. I understand that bugs can happen and with this system it is almost impossible to trouble shoot until I get back home to the Dog Station. And for the time it worked it was really good. I could see my cats play and listen to any suspicious noises. I strongly recommend!', 'Works well, we use it as a baby monitor! Premium functionality makes a big difference, though. Free version is very limited.', "Great idea, needs more tweaking. Love the ease of this and how you're enabling monitoring without the cost of other expensive equipment. Unfortunately it's a *huge* battery drain on phones (drains mine to low battery within an hour ) and unless you're keep the screen of the app open, it seems to 'check out' and then reconnect, so no way too know if it's monitoring. Please work on battery drain and keeping the app open and on. I'm not sure about the sensivity suitability yet but will feed back.", "Great app, but it's far too pricey for subscription. I can get a camera from Amazon for less than the yearly subscription price.", 'Barkio does exactly what it says on the tin! Very clear in both sound and video! Would definitely be signing up after my free trial!', 'This app is brilliant. Dont know how much it costs as im just using the free trial right now but its perfect, Simple, clear, reliable.', "Awesome app I I recommend if you're exploring your options don't skip this one trust me!", 'Amazing app. It works very well and has interesting features', 'I installed in a hurry, and it was simple and fast. Very nice app', 'This app is great for when you need to watch you pup however if you keep the TV on it will register your dog as being noisy.', "Disconnects from my laptop all the time so I can't even use it when I'm away from home which is the entire reason I got it.", "Love this app. Perfect to keep an eye on my cats when I'm away for the weekend.", 'We are on our first holiday with our Dog, and I remembered a friend recommended this app from a dog trainer. It is fabulous and offers us so much comfort to know our dog is settled when we are out!!']

title: Dog Hotel Tycoon
description:
Become a dog hotel tycoon, and create a world for your dog guests to enjoy!

CREATE A WORLD FOR YOUR DOG GUESTS TO ENJOY!
Start with a small dog hotel in a suburban area, and improve it to become the first 5+ star dog hotel! Create areas for your dogs to take naps, eat delicious snacks, play with each other, swim, excercise and much more! Anything to ensure the satisfaction of your dog guests!

WELCOME DOGS FROM ALL AROUND THE WORLD!
Become a dog hotel tycoon and accept more breeds as you grow your hotel, such as Corgi, Dachshund, Pug, Samoyed, Poodle, German Shepherd, Labrador, French Bulldog, English Bulldog, Basset Hound, Chiuahua, Chow Chow, Beagles, Shiba Inu, and many more. Each and every single dog will have their own unique character, behavior, wants and needs; and it is up to you to satisfy them!

TAKE YOUR DOGS TO DAILY DOG EVENTS!
Each day, you'll be able to take your dogs to the daily Dog Show, which is a physical obstacle challenge that will test the health & fitness of your dogs! 
There will also be a new Dog Quiz waiting for you each day, which will test your knowledge about dogs as well as teaching you interesting facts about them!

FEATURES
★ Easy to play game for every animal lover!
★ Cute Dogs with unique characteristics and lifelike behavior!
★ More than 80 dogs to have as guests, and more to come!
★ Fun rooms and items for your dogs to enjoy!
★ Send your dogs to Dog Shows!
★ Learn about dogs and earn rewards with the daily Dog Quiz!

If you love dogs, and incremental idle clicker games, you will love idle Dog Hotel Tycoon. As with all idle clicker games, you will never run out of things to do!

This game is free to play, but it contains items that can be purchased for real money. If you are having any issues with the game or have any feedback, you can always reach us at support@filgames.com

title: Zoosk - Social Dating App
description: ZOOSK IS THE TOP DATING APP, let us tell you why... More than 40 million singles worldwide have trusted Zoosk to find online dates or chat with new people, and create meaningful relationships and now it’s your turn! ENJOY THE BEST DATING EXPERIENCE POSSIBLE, come on board! • Looking for love, a casual partner, or to expand your professional network? We got you covered! • With Zoosk, whether you’re a lesbian, gay, bisexual, or straight, we can match you with local singles near you. Our international community of over 3 million active users is waiting for you. WHY ZOOSK OVER OTHER ONLINE DATING APPS? • We've just launched our new free livestreaming feature - Zoosk Live. Enjoy watching and starting global livestreams 24/7, plus meeting and dating other singles in real time. • We prioritize safe dating. Our Photo Verification tool is in place to give you confidence that the person you’re talking to looks like their profile picture. To ensure our members are who they say they are, we also provide a phone number and social media account verification. • With our SmartPick™ you can get better matches based on compatibility and preferences. Once you find someone you want to chat with, try one of our icebreakers, write a message*or even send a gift*! READY. SET. DATE. No more senseless swipes: download Zoosk dating app and get ready, because meeting someone is just a tap away. DISCOVER OUR AMAZING FREE FEATURES: All basic members can access these features: - Our new free livestreaming feature - Zoosk Live - See members’ pictures - Send Winks and Hearts - Use Carousel to discover new people BOOST YOUR DATES WITH OUR EXCLUSIVE FEATURES If you are ready to move on to the serious stuff, become a Zoosk subscriber so you can also: • Unlock Carousel matches • Boost your profile • Send gifts • Get Delivery Confirmation on messages • Chat with your connections • Unlock and connect with people who've viewed you • Say yes to and start chatting with your SmartPicks™ The Zoosk dating app is free to use. If you decide to upgrade or purchase one of our subscriptions here’s what you should know: • All subscriptions and upgrades like coins automatically renew unless you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription period without any limitations. • Turn off the auto-renewal through your account settings and your subscription and/or upgrades will expire at the end of their term • To learn more, read our Terms of Use Agreement: http://www.zoosk.com/tos and • Check our FAQs: http://zoosk.com/help. • See our Privacy Policy: www.zoosk.com/privacy and online dating safety guide at https://www.zoosk.com/safety. BUZZ AROUND ZOOSK ‘’ The dating service has made it really easy to start a profile, meet other users, and cast a wide net for potential matches.’’ - Mashable ‘’ Launched in 2007, Zoosk has become the toast of the online dating world’’ - AskMen Want to make your own opinion? Download the Zoosk dating app now and enjoy chatting with exciting people. Fun or connection, love is here! Follow us for dating and relationship tips: - Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Zoosk/ - Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/zoosk/ - Date Mix: https://www.zoosk.com/date-mix/ Your one in a million might be closer than you think. Download the Zoosk dating app for FREE and discover new singles in your area, connect with your matches based on common interests, and go on a date!
summary: For fun online dates - Match, chat & send virtual gifts to singles near you

comments: ["The account setup is great but the app itself functionality-wise is a mess. I can't even like a profile without it telling me that I need to verify my account even though I did it, multiple times via email. It's the same with the video verification as well I submit but then the same page appears over and over. I can't use basic functions, It's because of this that I won't be using this app. There's also a very limited selection as well as I've been seeing the same profiles over and over again.", "I heard good things about this app. I went and purchased the shortest subscription among only 3 choices it offered to handcuff me to in terms of subs. (3mo). I'd have liked a weekly option to try it without the long commitment. There's nothing wrong with the app itself. Only, I keep seeing the same online users over and over. After reaching out to dozens of them not a single one replied. The only good thing I've found is there are no bots. I cancelled the sub but still have over a month left.", 'The app is a complete waste of time unless you are willing to pay their monthly fees to see who liked you or send & read messages. So, unless you pay AND the person you wanted to communicate with also paid for the subscription you will be wasting your time. Also, if you do happen to join, you will see a green dot on a few profiles indicating they have logged on within the past few days. There are very few even when I expand the search criteria. An absolute waste of time.', 'I have been on here 2 months.....I paid to be able to talk and maybe meet someone. I am constantly having to verify myself. No one responds to messages or likes. The profiles for the smartpicks, you can barely see the pics people put up. I constantly have to change my search preferences and no preferences for the smartpicks. Honestly, the app really sucks!!!!', 'The app continuously crashes after about 2 mins of use. Very frustrating! Carousel is a useless tool as it doesn\'t take any of your preferences into account and you can\'t see how far away some is when choosing to "like" or not. If someone lives 500 miles away I wouldn\'t "like" them.', 'So frustrating, who are your developers and ux people??? Has to be one of the worst dating apps in navigation and usage... Same girls keep popping up first so you have to keep scrolling through them to get to the new ones, this is a 10 minute coding fix and no one thinks this is a problem??? And two options, remove conversation and remove connection, what the heck... And then some girls you only get one of those choices even when you have written them... Just horrible quality control', "Same notifications are being shown all the time. In Smartpick, you can't look at photos, only a tiny thumbnail of 1 picture. So how are you supposed to choose and teach the algorithm accurately about what you like?", "Customer service was good when I complained about a couple of things but other than that that's about as far as it goes. If anybody's actually real and close to you they certainly don't want to chat or me. I sent out 67 messages got a response from one. Pay the extra for premium messaging so they could answer me without worrying about it and they still didn't do that. Just like all the others it all comes down to money nonexistent profiles. Pretty much a waste of time.", "It's a free app you pay for... Ots free to download, setup etc then to even message yoi have to pay , the UI is absolute trash. Should not be allowed to have apps this predatory. So after trying it further just seems more and more like 99% if the interactions are fake. If not 30 seconds after I like someone they like back instantly but anyone I pass doesn't like it screams some marketing BS. Also £25PM? For any kind of basic app use? Yeah you need shutting down.", "Set up to keep you swiping, recommends users and hitting the red x does not make them go away so even if you just see the user profile Zoosk will alert them that you're in fact visiting their profile. So it looks like a bunch of people are viewing you. Carousel mode sucks because you have to say yes or no based on one pic and not able to visit their profile, smart pick sucks for the same reason, and the next date live feature is like something from some kind of onlyfans nightmare. DELETED", "This app is not worth it. I tried the 1 month purchase and I am extremely disappointed. No one ever response and the same few memeber for the example keep looking at my profile but nothing more. Hey I might not be the most attractive but come on. No activity anywhere .No one ever online it was a waste of money don't waste your hard earned money on this specific app.", 'The style works well. Carousel as others say, has potential, but broken. Why would I want to meet someone 500 miles away? App needs a search choice on activity, mostly dear in my demographic. Wish I knew how it worked better before wasting money subscribing. WE NEED A SEARCH OPTION FOR ACTIVITY ON APP!', "Hi good day to all. My name is Avion and this is the worst experience that I have had on this app, as a matter of fact, I have an account that can't be erased, thanks to someone who is using it. I have pressed unsubscribed, wrote to customer service, and still it hasn't been deleted. I find it very disturbing that this company has refused to delete my account, that someone else is using, only to their benefit (whose name is Sarah and apparently lives in Houston and I am from the Caribbean).", "I've met some good people on Zoosk, but your experience is probably dependent on your location. The Carousel is the worst. It matches based on pictures, does not filter for distance, and the app counts a Carousel view as a profile view. Otherwise, it's one of the better apps.", "Too many annoying notifications digging for clicks. Don't give you any way to choose which ones you get so you get 9/10 useless notifications just to get the one useful notification. Its like a predatory ad with their click bait. Oh ... and turning off notifications doesn't actually stop them. They just remove the information and send them anyway. Get some better coders.", "My account cannot be deleted. I can only deactivate. This is an absolute disgrace. Who do you think you are, keeping people's data after they've removed consent? There's a vague reference online to having to email the company to get your account deleted. No one should have to do this. Any other app just lets you delete whenever you want in app. Also, it's impossible to find an email address to contact! Oh, and FYI, I'm deleting because the app in general is terrible.", "Can't msg/reply or see msg unless you pay. They edit your bio taking out just the words they don't like. I've X people and still see them pop up. Any dating site that wants the cost of a phone card just to msg someone is unreasonable. They have the option of paying for the year for cheaper per month, but if they did a good job no one should search that long. The view profile is 🙃 scroll every pic before seeing info / bio if there even is a bio.", "Changing my review from two stars to one. Too bad there isn't a zero stars option. DO NOT WASTE YOUR MONEY ON THIS APP! This app constantly crashes and I have to reinstall every time I want to use it. All they want is your money. I paid for one month and still can't read messages from other users. If I decline or dismiss someone they'll show up the very next day. Most of the profiles that are too good to be true are bots. Don't walk away from this app, RUN!!!", "Horrible interface. Doesn't limit distance or necessarily show distance to potential matches in all is modes. Not very clear. Also seems to nickel and dime you after you have a subscription. Wouldn't recommend at all", 'Issue when you scroll over those who have "Viewed Me" it registers to the other person that you\'ve browsed their profile when you\'ve just scrolled past. This generates confusion as people think you\'re interested in them if you have to scroll past. Please fix this up so that the wrong message is not received.', 'There was no option to chat with anyone without having a paid subscription, so I went ahead & paid for 3 months, just to find out that\'s not the worst part. Men who I "X" out, indicating I\'m not interested in keep popping up & keep messaging me. Some getting increasingly more hostile that I\'m not responding. When I disconnect from matches, they still show up in my search, so I get to look at men who have ghosted me after dates. Overall I\'m displeased.', 'In my opinion, it seems like a scam , I have a team of people who check if these apps are legit , and it seems like some of the profiles are not legitimate. The same , you need to buy credits to chat with people , even when subbed , if you by credits , seem like it either an Ai , or a paid actor that response immediately, please comment if you had similar experience , having to by credits is a red flag lots of sites use the same model , this is all in my opinion.', 'I used to enjoy this service before covid. Now, there are tons of inactive accounts, I know for sure I used to date some of these ladies who are now moved or in a relationship. I wish they required you to long on to keep the account active and disable those accounts who havent login for years. Hardly anyone responds to you. You have to pay just to message anyone or pay for the feature to let people message you back. My area has no members who are active. I felt baited to pay for a subscription.', "It's okay.. I'm truly wishing that the possibilities of dating these amazing interesting guys, just happen to live a very long distance from me... Sad! So, I'm willing to travel a bit.. but it's going to be challenging. I'm hoping this could work out & I find my partner to grow old with, make some wonderful memories.", 'Pretty good app overall. However, Carousel is a totally worthless and distracting but prominent aspect. Who can pick who they "like" without a location? This is after all a "dating app" and if a person lives too far away to "date" what the heck difference does it make? If a member lists the maximum distance they are willing to consider, the app should respect that even if it means there are only a few matches. I can always change my search criteria.', "If I x out someone...they shouldn't keep popping up. Give new people!!! Few glitches have been solved...(6/23) Wish I would have read reviews first. Friend of mine met her husband on here so had to try it. *Click a notification and it doesn't take you to it. *People 500+ miles away! *when you back up on the page it takes you to the home screen rather than who you were looking at.", "It's extremely frustrating to be connected with people so far away. I have my search preference for 50 miles but it still shows me people much farther away. I hate Carousel! You can't see how far they are. I have blocked multiple members because of distance but they keep appearing in my search and also on carousel.", "Yeah, this site sucks. You pay the subscription, but you still have to pay for everything else. You see the same people on your searches. It doesn't tell you if the members even use their account, so it's full of unused accounts. I've seen the same people that probably haven't been on for months. You have to pay to see if someone reads your message. No native american ethnicity choice. The flaws are countless.", 'August 13 2023 So far, this has been a brutal experience. I just joined last night and bought a membership plan. But every time I tried to contact someone, it said, "Subscribe to send." I checked my bank & the payment went through. What the hell?! Now, this morning, I\'m getting messages saying I have to have internet to use the app. Again, what the hell?! I sent an email about the situation, but you guys are taking your sweet time to respond. I\'m so turned off by this! Just give my money back!', "Tried the site out for a month, it would have been smarter for me to flush my money down the toilet! This is the absolutely worst dating site if you ask me and I've tried a few of them. You keep getting interest from women you do not want to get interest from! And you see them over and over and over again. There are far too many things wrong with Zoosk for me to detail, the best advice I can give is don't waste your money or your time.", "Some hiccups sometimes you can't use it freely or are able to see the profiles when is important. Make sure you are talking to a real person, be open to make so friends and who knows. You might be able to find the person that you are looking for!", "Miserable user experience. They charge too much for what you get and constantly ask for more money. There is no way to search for new users without going through the hundreds of users you already have seen. Most users don't respond, which makes me wonder if they are real accounts. Do bot install. Stay away!", "It's not bad however, the amount of fake profiles is unfortunate yet, this is my 3rd time back because out of say 100, 2 that I've met which each turned into a relationship that lasted over several yrs were amazing & worth it. In fact I'm still friends w then after our relationship ended. 🤷🏻\u200d♂️", "This is about the worst dating app I've used. Hardly any matches in my area. Many of the daily Smart Picks are 100 miles away from me! Those I have matched with don't want to engage in a back and forth conversation. So frustrating!", "Paid for a one month subscription and still denied access to perks of a subscription. Why pay for something when I'm getting the same deal for free? I definitely won't be subscribing again or will I'll be keeping my account active.", 'App is okay. Routinely gives you "views" to keep you interacting with the app though those people may not be actively viewing your profile. The carousel portion is frustrating as you can\'t see the person\'s location and their proximity to you. Lots of "likes" from people way too far away. Met a really good guy on the app and I\'m grateful for that. Watch out for fake profiles/scammers.', 'Terrible app. It constantly states it has no internet connection. It does! All the time. So, I have to uninstall, then reinstall. Absolute pain!', 'WASTE OF TIME AND MONEY! Terrible site. Messages keep failing and being deleted. Site keeps locking up. Customer service is not fixing it. Keeps showing same people even after Ive said no dismiss. Cant block the creeps. Does not work. WASTE OF MONEY! No way to get refund for garbage app.', 'Literally liars. Don\'t fall for it. This app fabricated a message from a profile I liked so I got a message notification. I pay to see the message and it\'s "Thanks for the greeting! Send me a message to start chatting!"', "If you tried to make a worse dating app than this I don't think you could. From fake profiles to delayed messages to would you like to pay extra to see if a message you sent has been read by recipient. Garbage in every way. 0 stars. Designed to keep you paying and paying and paying. Originally a Facebook product. ."]

title: Merge Dogs
description:
Merge your dogs, build the ultimate dog racing team and win the race!

Do you have what it takes to be the best dog racer out there? Start by getting small puppies, then upgrade them into bigger faster dogs and earn lots of money!

Features:
- Over 20 different dog breeds to discover including shiba inu, corgi, golden retriever, pug, french bulldog, chihuahua, poodle, beagle, dachshund, dalmatian, dobermann, rottweiler and lots more!
- Idle earnings. Gain coins even while you are away or offline.

Manage your team of super fast dogs. Start your dog racing team now and become a champion!
summary: Build your doggy team and win the race!

comments: ['The design of everything is very simple and cute. The animations and feel of it is very happy. You do have to wait, but the animations help for the wait time since the animation entertains you as you wait. A very fun game overall. Perfect for people who like achievin', "This game was fun at first but it starts playing you when your about the finish the game like not giving you your money and taking your good dogs and replacing them with bad ones ( for example there are 5 pages and I was on the husky on the 4th page and they replaced it with a dog from the fourth page) which may not seem like a big deal but the higher the dog the more epband money so replacing it so you get less and have to wait months for a new dog This game is just impractical don't waste time", "Starts off fun but after you gather a few dog species it becomes very difficult to move in to the next species. especially because the money you gather while the app is off is limited. Fun but has more potential. I've dropped it now.", 'Very addictive. As a dog person this game is perfect for me. If you are a dog person you should download Merge Dogs! The graphics are great. So many new types of dogs to collect. I have used the 2x speed. It is one of the best money makers in the game. The 5 star review has been earned. Download right now!', 'It\'s ok... a bit confusing at first figuring out what to do and what the purpose is of having the dogs run laps in circles... keep thinking they\'re going to get tired and get thirsty... thought it was going to be more like a "real merge three" game, not merge two or more. I do however enjoy "creating" the new dog species! it is original, but it needs improvements overall. gets repetitive and lacks incentive after awhile. but I think many people would like it with a clear explanation of what it is', "Really good game it gets kind of boring because it's just a loop you get a dog you merge the dog then again. I think it's a very good game though.", "I love everything but could get lil boring rarely adds don't have to pay money it's good 😊 one thing though there is bugs like sometimes one of the dogs was tiny and hard to see maybe see what's wrong? I recommend the game though ;)", "This game is amazing! There are rarely ads, and the dogs are super cute! The only thing is that it gets boring sometimes but that's okay! PLEASE download this app!!!", "Alright, so, I really enjoyed this game at first. It was super fun, really cute, definitely addictive. However... I'm about halfway through the catalogue both for the grass track and the snow track, and now it's boring. It takes too long to get to the bigger dogs, since you only get two hours of away time. There's an upgrade for two more but... Do I wanna pay to still barely be able to buy two dogs at a higher tier? There just isn't enough to do to keep it fun. Good for a while tho!", "This game started out lots of fun and I was always excited to see all the new dogs you could unlock but as you get into the later stages, sometimes my best dogs are randomly deleted and replaced, I have been playing for a long while so it takes weeks and months to get a new dog but they keep getting replaced before I can get a new dog, it does it often and it's impossible to progress through the game at this point. It takes away from the cute aspects. Example; Lost my Samoyed for a Dalmatian.", 'This is a good mindless game to pass the time, it helped me fall asleep. A tutorial would have been nice, I played for days before I figured it to click on the dogs and rabbits. The look of the pit bull was disappointing. All the dogs are very happy looking except him. The devs had an opportunity to put the beautiful dogs in a positive light and they took a wrong turn with it. Last, I beat both levels in just over a week, more levels would be awesome. I am uninstalling for now.', 'okay. i love the colours and the art style used! they really compliment each other and make the game enjoyable. i REALLY like the ability to buy certain dogs as you level up!! that makes it a lot easier but still challenging enough to keep playing! one thing i would like would be the ability to purchase outfits for certain dogs, with in game watch to earn ads, and ingame cash from the dogs. overall this game is great ✌️', "Addicting and fun, until the ads stopped working, except, of course, the ads that provide zero benefits, which also happen extremely often now. I tried restarting the app multiple times. No luck. Fix this soon or I will delete. I already had to skip a bunch of rewards that I can't get anymore because I could have gotten them by watching an ad. Not satisfied at all... :( UPDATE: They sort of fixed the issue. I can get a reward from a video once, then I need to restart the app, so 3 from 2 stars.", 'This game is great! So fun! When i downloaded it at first i was a bit skeptical thinking about how hard it would be to get more dogs when i got pretty far in the game but i actually enjoy the way they set it up greatly! How you let the dogs run to collect more coins. Its creative and a good way to not run out as well as you dont have to buy coins or watch ads for them! 😁 Love the game! Addicting, easy, and loads of fun!', "The game isn't really challenging for the mind. Buy a dog, for ever increasing prices, or wait for a free one. Let it run on the track to make money. Combine two of same to get another dog, of a higher level. That one will get you the same income as the two old dogs, only faster, so merging dogs is usually worth it. The rest (free dogs, 20% discount, double speed) is click bait, you get something and the designers earn money. But in the ent, it's surprisingly funny and addictive. I quite like it.", 'I love this game the only thing I wish they could improve is how long you have to merge the dogs. Anyways the whole rest of the game is great!😊', 'This game is amazing and I love it. I stayed up late playing this game!! It is awesome!! I recommend it to whoever is looking at this. If you like offline games... This is for you! All you have to do to get rid of the ads is turn off your mobile data (if you have that) or turn off your interet! Then no ads. It does load, but dont worry. This is a 5 star rating!!! Love it so much. Again you can always get rid of the ads by turning off internet or mobile data. Anyway, thats my review! 🥰🐶🐕🐕\u200d🦺', 'MAGNIFIC DOG MERGE GAME 🐕 good work. Thank you! 🐩 I was about to finish the game, so I uninstall it to restart it, so much it is relaxing and awesome . 💕', "This game was fun but you need to add a tutorial for new player's but it does help me fall asleep.", "its a cute game, and the dogs models are adorable. it has a short, simple tutorial which is nice. I just don't like how long it takes to upgrade to the next dog. it's a slow-paced game compared to most idle games but that's not a horrible thing. the in-game purchases are also a bit overpriced. I love it as a time passer, but I'm uninstalling.", "It's a cute game but it just feels so plain and basic. At least in Merge Planes you could get boosters, etc for the track, and there was a leader board. I don't want to watch fifty million ads just to make my dogs go faster, etc. And they don't even go that fast with the ads. Plus, the ads don't always work. You need to do more to this otherwise boring game.", "It's a cute app, but is it fun? sort of, at your lowest stage it's fun and you merge but soon it becomes into a log on, collect reward, buy more dogs, close app, repeat. I do like that the ads aren't forced but I do watch them anyway. 1 video to double my 2 billion? sure why not. most people won't like this but I do like grind fest games. so it's cute and it's grindy, following the popular trend of merge apps. with not anything else thrown in to spice it up, that's about it.", "The cutest game I've played so far. The game is very simple and really good for destressing. Animation is cute, and I get excited every time I get a new dog. I'm unable to play ads though so I can't redeem other features. But overall the game is just really chill and enjoyable.", 'This is a great game. But I have a problem, my progress keeps getting lost! I was at the level were I unlocked the sheltie but I come back the next day and it is gone, i still unlocked it in the book of dogs but did not have it on the track. I probably wont get a reply or a bot reply I just hope that this problem gets fixed.', 'I wanted to like this game, but there are a few things that turned me off. First of which was the farther I got in the game, the speed in which the dogs speed around the track literally made me sick. Visually it was disturbing and maybe should come with a warning. The second thing is why is the pitbull the only vicious looking design. All the other breeds look super sweet and friendly. I think the designers are perpetuating an unfair bias.', 'Fun game, but a while ago(long time) i had much progress on the game when it randomly crashed and wouldnt open, this went on for a week until i gave up. When it finally let me play it deleted most of my progress. It is now crashing again and im thinking it will do what it did previously, nice app, but please fix it so it doesnt delete progress, or atleast let us save it somehow.(im on latest version so that cant be why.)', "This app is so so cute and fun!! But it has a bug that happened to me twice. I don't know how that happened but it was in the snow place that my fastest dog lost two times. So I have to use more money and it's so hard because of slower income because of the bug. And also the away time says I'll get my income for 4 hours when I don't use the app but it's just actually 4 minutes. I was supposed to earn at least a trillion in 4 hours but it just gives me 50 billion. It's a fun game though. = )", 'Stopped playing it last year because constant crashes made it impossible to play. Felt the urge to play it again and glad to see that the crashes have been fixed! Cute and fun way to pass the time!', "Thia game is an adorable idle merge game, there's enough factors that go into each dog that give the game more depth than expected, and I love that it has multiple worlds or zones that play at the same time. The only thing I think the game is lacking is a more solid active playing aspect, I'd like to see some kind of minigame alongside the idle aspects, but it's still a complete game that is worth your time.", "Like the game as a way to kill time. Got to Pom, and it looked like it was floating? Thought nothing of it and continued to play, only to find that when I got a 2nd Pom, they wouldn't merge. Closed the app and restarted - my 2nd Pom is going and the Pom I have has been taken off the track. This has happened twice now.", "I think that the game was very simple and easy. It was very short thought. You barley got any dogs and most other breeds can be left out. I know it is kinda tricky to find nonpopular breeds of dogs, but I still think it's great. To the game creaters, you should make one with cats and the different breeds also. I think the game was very cute and I enjoyed it.", "well.. I liked this game, it was fun to merge the lil doggos to get more doggos. BUT. After getting over half the doggos in the regular one and almost completing the snow one, the game continuously crashes. I open it and not even 2 seconds later it crashes. Not enough time for me to do anything. It's super frustrating because I'm just so close to finishing it. I put a lot of effort into this.", "It's an easy game to pass the time with. But a few too many ads for my liking. It's ok to have ads for bonus things like the 2x speed but i don't like that one automatically plays for 5 seconds when i close the buy-a-dog screen.", 'The music is great👍 and very happy 😊! I love the dogs 🐕 ❤ and they are very cute 😍! the racing is adorable ❤!', "great game, I'm enjoying unlocking so many great breeds of dogs. the ads are a bit much but I'm not even mad considering you can use it for speeding up money, leveling up to a higher breed when using money, but it randomly comes up when you arent clicking anything that would start an ad and it gets quite annoy when an ad appears for no reason.", 'after a while you can no longer watch ads because the dogs are going so fast, so every time an ad tried to pop up, you have to watch your dogs run behind a loading screen for about 5-10 seconds.. I miss the "watch an ad to make them go 2x as fast!" or "watch an ad to get the next level of dog!" so yeah, the process is becoming a lot slower but I still love to poke the doggos. its actually quite addicting considering it gets laggy after a while', "Love it! Super cute and fun! However!!! It doesn't do a good job at conveying some things. Things like the X2 multiplier lasts 2 minutes and 30 seconds. And it doesn't tell you how much your max away is. All it tells you is that you'll get 2 more hours of max away if you pay them real cash money. A bit unnecessarily annoying.", 'I love the game so much it is a cute doggy game I love I how you can get different dogs my favorite so far that I have is my best one the dalmation. I love this game! Update) I would like a "Save" feature. I recently uninstalled (For storage and realized "oh fu-".) Reinstalled and lost my progress. If you could add a save feature so i can reload my work would be nice, If its already there then ;-;-', "Got months of playtime out of this. Simple idler with ROCK SOLID design. Art is adorable, control is intuitive, and lots of dogs means it last you a while. A few design elements raise its quality of life as time goes on: The quick-buy button (not real $) for the smallest dog eventually moves up the ladder as you unlock new dogs, so merge chains don't become impossibly long slogs. And you can always tap the dogs on your track for a little extra speed/cash. My new benchmark for merge-style games.", 'A Great Game! So much fun! At first when i downloaded it looked skeptical and confusing thinking about how hard it would be to get more dogs but when i got a bit far in the game, i actually enjoyed the way it was set up. Love the game, Addicting, easy and lots of funs.']

title: Lua — Dating With Depth
description:
Lua’s purpose is deepening intimacy, connecting people to Love. Skip small talk and connect deeply with like-minded people from conscious communities.

Designed by intimacy and relationships experts, Lua helps you go deep with your match. The intentional and swipe-free design makes online dating feel more like a playful mystery and less like online shopping.

Lua is open to people of all genders, sexual identities, and relationship styles, so you can explore your desires and be your authentic self. No masks, just real intimacy (into-me-you-see).

Features include:

• Sharings
- Post answers to deep, playful, and flirty Sharings questions via text, photo, and voice
- Scroll answers (and profile photos) of potential matches
- Tap ‘like’ and match with people you’re interested in, then discover each other deeply ‘in the mystery’ (you’ll know you liked them, but you won’t know exactly who it is till you ‘reveal’)

• Meet in Mystery 
Set your preferences for who you’d like to meet and Lua will match you with someone special, anonymously. No swiping, filters and superficial stuff to drive the match, just a sense of magic. This is what we call ‘meeting in the dark’. Let Lua surprise you…

• Skip Small Talk & Connect Deeply
Designed by leaders in the personal growth and relationships fields, Lua helps you get to know your match through guided deep and playful questions, before you finally reveal your profile. It’s both a playful self-reflection and a way to really get to know this special someone.

• The Action Starts With An Avatar
You select the animal archetype you want to be represented by. Depending on your mood or what you want to embody, you can update your avatar as you please.

• Sparks: Choose to Reveal
After you’ve both answered Lua’s questions and gotten to know each other more deeply, you can mutually reveal your true identity. From there, you can choose to journey together ‘in the light’.

• Inspirational personal growth and relationship tips
Intentional relationships can be a vehicle for personal growth. In between matches, Lua shares tips from experts in the personal development and relating field to help you connect to yourself and others.

• A culture of authenticity and trust
Lua’s intentional design creates a culture of authentic communication, desire and enthusiastic consent, shame-free expression, maturity and kindness. Ghosting is not how we roll on Lua.

• Get Matched With Like-Minded People
Lua is invite-only, so you’ll be connecting with epic beings who are also intentional, devoted to growth, and exploring authentic relationships and lifestyles. You’re with your people.

title: Tamadog - Puppy Pet Dog Games
description:
Have you ever dreamed about having a dog? About a cute little puppy that you will take care of… Dreams come true with dog life simulator Tamadog. It is your new virtual pet. Care for it, love and make it happy.

Your new virtual friend 🐩

Don’t hesitate and get a dog right now. Such a lovely, charming and cute puppy, who likes having fun, eating yummies and taking selfies. You’ll never get bored with it. Discover the Tamadog’s bright world with a variety of exciting adventures in dog town.

Meet your new virtual friend in the Tamagotchi dog game. Just look at these cute eyes that will melt your heart… Play talking puppy games, give it delicious treats, take it for walks and just have fun all day long. Pet dog games are made for love. Give your doggy all your love and it will definitely love you back.  

Check out the Tamadog pet simulator and enjoy taking care of your little faithful friend. Imagine that you are playing dog sim Tamagotchi - now the gameplay is in the real pet world… It's a dream come true.

TAMADOG COOL FEATURES:

🐶 VIRTUAL PET IN YOUR REAL HOME. Don't forget to give your pet care everyday. Feed it, clean and play with it. You can play both 3D and AR games mode. Allow the app to use a phone camera and your puppy will appear right inside your house. 
🐕 RAISE A SMART PET. Record voice commands and train your dog. From “sit down” to “break dance” – you can teach your dog lots of cool tricks. Talk to your friend. You doggy is so sociable and eager to learn. That is my dog - you will say proudly. 
📸 CAPTURE AMUSING MOMENTS. Take cute selfies with your puppy and its dog life, make hilarious videos and share them with friends.
🎰 UNLOCK NEW LEVELS. Keep raising a happy pet, play dog games and enjoy extra activities as a reward.
👗 DRESS UP YOUR PUPPY. Stylish suits for agile male pups and fancy dresses for fluffy girl puppies - dress up your little friend trendy.
🥰 ULTIMATE CUTENESS. Your new friend loves you and goes head over heels when you rub its belly. Can you imagine that your doggy will gladly lick your nose anytime you move the screen closer? All possible with animal games. 
🎮 MINI-GAMES. Your puppy is asleep or you just need to relax from the daily routine? Try yourself in exciting mini-games in a dog simulator and set your records. There are a lot of puppy games for free for any taste: shooting bubbles is just as entertaining as healing and grooming your dog in diverse and enjoyable lovely pets mini-games.

The only virtual dog that looks like and feels like a real dog. Feed it, pet it, play with it. Take it wherever you want, your doggy with its pet’s world is always at hand. You’ll never get bored with it.

Show everyone how adorable your puppy is. Try to catch all the bright moments spending together with your virtual friend in puppy games. Take amusing and funny selfies with your AR dog and create your own photo album full of happy memories.

Your pet is tired? Take a break - play mini puppy games free to not feel bored. Challenge yourself in exciting Match 3 games, while your pet is resting. Discover more than 300 levels of the game and try to finish all them to earn special gifts for your talking dog. Play dog games for free and make your pet happier.

TRY PREMIUM ACCESS 
Subscribe for Premium and get unlimited access to all the AR dog game features:
🍖 Unlock all premium items
🍖 Unlock AR mode
🍖 Free daily coins and diamonds

Time has come! Get a puppy with the Tamadog pet games. Love it, care for it and make sure it is becoming your best friend. 💗
summary: Have fun with cute puppy games and raise your charming dog!
